{"tid":649978,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[鬼打鬼]油麻地南亞漢遭同鄉持鎅刀行劫　失銀包金鏈","createTime":"2018-05-02T02:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T04:59:26.000Z","uid":131259,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"02780a469bdd4cdb58158afea65cef16cb89fdf6","tid":649978,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:41:21.000Z","msg":"油麻地發生行劫案。凌晨1時許，兩名南亞裔男子在油麻地寶靈街一間便利店購買飲品，離開時於門外遭另外兩名蒙面南亞裔男子以鎅刀指嚇，其中一名29歲事主被劫去放有4000元現金的銀包及戴於身上、價值1.6萬元的金鏈。賊人得手後逃去無蹤。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場調查，在附近一帶兜截，惟未有發現。案件交由油尖警區刑事調查隊第三隊跟進，警方正追緝一名非華裔男子，身高約1.6米，瘦身材，案發時戴鴨舌帽及口罩，身穿藍色上衣及藍色牛仔褲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180502/s00001/1525224640926\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180502%2Fs00001%2F1525224640926&d=U%2FmuvXwI1vujrWW5Gmd3hIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=3f09ca1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180502%2Fs00001%2F1525224640926&h=bc795d1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180502/s00001/1525224640926</a><br />\n<br />\n隊友可能知隻蝻琴晚食完大茶飯<br />\n近近地直接搶佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94d500eb4874f585be55dc79f8b09276a9e4dc6","tid":649978,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T03:49:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51fb72167a4274208157d05bbe99888476549687","tid":649978,"uid":156005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:02:26.000Z","msg":"好心d蝻返去自已國家行劫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fbf4fee0b52b6731c455baca411e9b966710cf","tid":649978,"uid":37715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:04:06.000Z","msg":"ape don't kill ape"},{"pid":"0e7554d0c0cb49e5